<h1>Scrambled Eggs</h1>
<p>Eggs are one of my favourite foods, Here i a recipe for deliciously rich scramled eggs.</p>

<h2>Ingredients</h2>
<ul>
	<li>2 eggs</li>
	<li>1tbs butter</li>
	<li>2tbs scream</li>
</ul>

<h2>Method</h2>
<ol>
	<li>Melt butter in a frying pan over a medium head</li>
	<li>Gently mix the eggs and cream in a bowl</li>
	<li>Once butter has melted add cream and eggs</li>
	<li>Using a spatula fold the eggs from the edge of the pan to the center every 20 seconds (as if you are making an omelette)</li>
	<li>When the eggs are still moist remove from the heat (it will coninue to cook on the plate until severd)</li>
</ol>

